trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to a tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when an <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Contém os dados enviados para um serviço de controlo a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução quando um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> é correspondido.

trans-unit.source: It is also used in the return list of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*> property.
trans-unit.target: Também é utilizado na lista de retorno de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>propriedade.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends an ActivityTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Quando a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução corresponde a um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>num <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, envia um ActivityTrackingRecord para o serviço de controlo sobre o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>associados a esse serviço de controlo.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is needed on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: O serviço de controlo pode realizar é necessária qualquer ação sobre os dados no registo de controlo.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Guid>que identifica o <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> da atividade principal da atividade associada com o evento de estado de atividade.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.DateTime>que indica a data e hora do evento de estado de atividade associada com o registo de controlo.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.target: ActivityType é definido pelo tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de anotações associados a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> foi correspondentes.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é definida pelo runtime infraestrutura de controlo.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations that are associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that corresponds to this tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> que contém as anotações que estão associadas a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> que corresponde a este registo de controlo.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list that contains any data extracted from the workflow for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma lista que contém todos os dados extraídos de fluxo de trabalho para o <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> foi correspondentes.

trans-unit.source: When an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>é correspondido, tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura pode extrair dados da instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The data to be extracted is specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Os dados a ser extraído são especificados por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain two kinds of objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the activity status event; and, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>pode conter dois tipos de objetos: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objetos especificar dados do membro a ser extraído da atividade associada com o evento de estado de atividade; e, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objetos especificar dados do membro a ser extraído da atividade raiz do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Both of these extract types can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Ambos os tipos de extrair também pode especificar anotações devem ser devolvidos com os dados extraídos.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates each piece of extracted data and its associated annotations in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>, and adds this <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> to Body.
trans-unit.target: A infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução encapsula cada peça de dados extraídos e respetivos anotações associadas num <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>e adiciona- <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>ao corpo.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é definida pelo runtime infraestrutura de controlo.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> objects each of which contains a single piece of extracted data and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Uma lista de <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> objetos, cada um dos quais contém um único conjunto de dados extraídos e respetivos anotações associadas.

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a data e hora em que ocorreu o evento de estado de atividade.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.DateTime>é a hora de Greenwich (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.DateTime>valor.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order in the workflow instance of the activity status event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica a ordem na instância de fluxo de trabalho do evento de estado de atividade que correspondeu a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the relative order of the event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> within the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder indica a ordem relativa do evento que correspondeu a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>dentro de instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder é exclusivo dentro de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho, mas não é garantido ser sequenciais.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder é definido pelo tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates the order of the activity status event in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Um valor que indica a ordem do evento de estado atividade na instância de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the execution status of the activity associated with this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o estado de execução da atividade associada a este <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A workflow instance only emits activity status events when the execution status of an activity instance changes.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância de fluxo de trabalho emite apenas eventos de estado de atividade quando o estado de execução de uma instância de atividade é alterado.

trans-unit.source: Therefore an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> can only be matched when an activity execution status change occurs.
trans-unit.target: Por conseguinte um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>só pode ser correspondido quando ocorre uma alteração de estado de execução de atividade.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus contains the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName> that triggered the match and caused the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> to be sent.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus contém o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>que acionou a correspondência e causou o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>seja enviado.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: It reflects the current status of the activity instance.
trans-unit.target: Este reflete o estado atual da instância de atividade.

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatus is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatus é definido pelo tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Um do <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> valores.

trans-unit.source: Context of the parent activity.
trans-unit.target: Contexto da atividade principal.
